you won't see me for smoke.

1097
00:57:15,140 --> 00:57:17,058
And what I tell her
will put the kibosh on your

1098
00:57:17,059 --> 00:57:19,644
buttercups and daisies romance,
tout de suite!

1099
00:57:19,645 --> 00:57:21,646
