1110
00:57:46,630 --> 00:57:49,173
Yeah, well, that was then.
Now is now.

1111
00:57:49,174 --> 00:57:51,258
What do you want me to do, Belle?

1112
00:57:51,259 --> 00:57:55,346
For a start, you can move
